title: Lithuania Core Consumer Prices
description: Core Consumer Prices in Lithuania increased to 131.04 points in September from 128.57 points in August of 2022. Core Consumer Prices in Lithuania averaged 92.68 points from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 131.04 points in September of 2022 and a record low of 61.45 points in January of 1996. This page provides - Lithuania Core Consumer Prices- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: EUROSTAT
